data.description: Come home to this newly remodeled work of art as the picturesque ambiance of the neighborhood draws you in. As you make your way in be greeted at the porch with a sense of safety and zen like appeal. Walk in and experience the white appeal of colors that appeal to your sense of purity. You can have TWO living areas if you choose! The high ceilings and the tempting view of the top floor. Indulge yourself and go up the wrought iron stairs and wooded staircase to THREE plush rooms with a master bedroom that boasts a seating area. With an oversized bathroom and tub, you are in a private escape. With so much appeal this home is best seen than described.
